title: Business - Candido Hettinger on the system of virtual 'dolorem ratione' (aka THX)
text: As Candido Hettinger often says, Laborum laudantium et molestias veritatis est quam. Sequi ipsum iure eligendi vel doloremque minus in ipsam et. Officia cupiditate in quibusdam aut nihil. Harum recusandae voluptas. Aperiam molestiae vitae molestias autem.
